high_descs: go to refrigerator to the right
pick up tomato from out of refrigerator, close refrigerator
go to sink to the left
put tomato in sink, turn on water, turn off water, pick up tomato from sink
go to white bin in between sink and refrigerator
anns.task_desc: place chilled, washed tomato in white bin

high_descs: Go forward to stand in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick up the tomato and shut the door of the fridge.
Go left and turn to face the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick up the tomato again.
Go to the right and face the trash can.
Put the tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in the sink.

high_descs: pick up tomato from inside fridge
wash tomato in sink, pick up tomato from sink
walk slightly right to face garbage bin
anns.task_desc: put a washed tomato into a garbage bin
